OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FSir has criticised the PM for the
OL,7,Fgovernment's announcement of a ban on
OL,8,F"colourful lanyards" in the civil
OL,9,Fservice, accusing of acting like a
OL,10,F"jumped up milk monitor".
OL,12,FThe Labour leader said Mr Sunak had
OL,13,Fbeen focusing too much on "the war
OL,14,Fagainst lanyards", rather than on
OL,15,Fissues like the "prison system in
OL,16,Fchaos".
