OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FDiscussions around rainbow lanyards
OL,7,Fhave swirled in Westminster since
OL,8,Fgovernment minister Esther McVey
OL,9,Fannounced a ban on rainbow-coloured
OL,10,Fand other "random" lanyards in the
OL,11,Fcivil service, because she said
OL,12,Fthey're an expression of "political
OL,13,Fviews".
OL,15,FSome members of the civil service
OL,16,Fchoose to wear rainbow lanyards,
OL,17,Fsometimes to indicate support for
OL,18,FLGBTQ+ rights, or to show support for
OL,19,Fthe NHS.
