OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FDuring her speech at the Centre for
OL,7,FPolicy Studies, Ms McVey who is
OL,8,Finformally known as the "common sense
OL,9,Fminister" said: "People want their
OL,10,Fpublic servants to be getting on with
OL,11,Fthe jobs of making their lives better."
OL,13,F"The lanyards worn to carry security
OL,14,Fpasses shouldn't be a random pick and
OL,15,Fmix, they should be a standard design
OL,16,Freflecting that we're all members of
OL,17,Fthe government delivering for the
OL,18,Fcitizens of the UK," she said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/12
