OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FDuring Prime Minister's Questions, Sir
OL,7,FKeir mocked the PM over the lanyard
OL,8,Fdebate: "On Monday the prime minister
OL,9,Ftreated us to his seventh relaunch in
OL,10,Feighteen months, he vowed to take on
OL,11,Fthe dangers that threaten the country.
OL,12,FSo it was good to see the minister for
OL,13,Fcommon sense immediately take up that
OL,14,Fmantle, by announcing a vital
OL,15,Fcrackdown on the gravest of threats -
OL,16,Fcolourful lanyards."
