OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FIn response to the attack by Sir Keir,
OL,7,FMr Sunak doubled down the comments by
OL,8,Fhis common sense minister, saying
OL,9,F"civil service impartiality is an
OL,10,Fimportant principle that we're right
OL,11,Fto support. Perhaps he should ask his
OL,12,Fchief of staff about that".
OL,14,FThe Labour leader's chief of staff Sue
OL,15,FGray was a senior civil servant before
OL,16,Fjoining Sir Keir's team.
