OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FThe guidance said the civil service's
OL,7,Fdiversity and inclusion strategy was
OL,8,Faimed at ensuring such values were
OL,9,F"mainstream", while adding there was
OL,10,Fno requirement for "homogeneity or
OL,11,Fconformity of belief or views".
OL,13,FIt also said that while civil servants
OL,14,F"must have a shared goal to tackle
OL,15,Fdiscrimination and prejudice, views on
OL,16,Fhow to practically address issues
OL,17,Frelating to diversity and inclusion
OL,18,Fare varied".
