OL,3,C'The war against lanyards': Starmer
OL,4,Cmocks PM over 'ban' on rainbow lanyards
OL,6,FThe guidance advised civil servants
OL,7,Fagainst "presenting subjective views
OL,8,For theories relating to diversity and
OL,9,Finclusion as accepted fact or as the
OL,10,Fposition of their organisation".
OL,12,FIn a written statement published at
OL,13,Fthe end of the Commons sitting day on
OL,14,FTuesday, Ms McVey said: "The guidance
OL,15,Fmakes clear that civil servants must
OL,16,Fnot allow their personal political
OL,17,Fviews to determine their actions or
OL,18,Fany advice they give related to
OL,19,Fdiversity and inclusion in any part of
OL,20,Ftheir employment."
