OL,6,FDuring PMQs Sir Keir Starmer also
OL,7,Fattacked the PM over overcrowing in
OL,8,Fprisons during PMQs, after a was
OL,9,Fextended in February.
OL,11,F"Are any of the prisoners he's letting
OL,12,Fout early considered to be high
OL,13,Frisk?", the Labour leader asked.
OL,15,FMr Sunak responded by insisting "no-
OL,16,Fone will be put on the scheme if
OL,17,Fthey're deemed a threat to the public."
